data.description: UPDATE: Seller will provide $6,000 for closing cost or upgrades. This 5-bedroom 3.5-bath home is an "as is" estate sale property that needs some repairs and updates including carpet and painting. There will be no repairs done by the Seller before the closing. This home is conveniently located in Bridgestone Village in Conyers GA. Minutes away from shopping, eating and The Georgia International Horse Park. IMPORTANT NOTE: The owner has a court appointed Personal Representative that has never occupied the property. The Personal Representative cannot provide HOA information, a Sellers Property Disclosure, or help with utility connections for inspections or any needed repairs. The house is being sold in "as is" condition and there are Seller Required Special Stipulations that must be included in all offers. The Seller Required Special Stipulations are provided in the Documents section of this MLS. The Personal Representative says we can accept offers with a 90-day closing timeline to allow for final review and approval by the Probate Court.
